data.description: Welcome to this beautiful single story nestled on a corner lot in the sought-out master planned community of Providence Village. A charming front porch welcomes you inside this updated home with a neutral freshly painted interior. A wonderful flex space is situated in the center of the home and could be used as a formal dining room or office. Enjoy preparing home-cooked meals in the fully equipped kitchen with stainless steel appliances, ample counter-top space and two breakfast bars. Make your way into the open concept living area complete with a relaxing wood burning fireplace and access to the covered patio and recently sodded backyard. The primary suite offers plenty of privacy from the secondary bedrooms and offers a large bath with jetted tub, dual sinks, separate shower and walk-in closet. Providence Village offers incredible amenities to suit every lifestyle with a Resort style pool, parks, playgrounds and much more! Unlock and enjoy!
